{
  "stem": "11274.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We walked all the way as fast as we could after this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Mom was standing outside and waiting, and shaking like this, and so was Danka.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think at that time Zosia was still home, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're waiting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, saved a life once.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For one time, not for long, though.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then those two officers-- later I heard rumors that Hans Joksch-- I didn't see him afterwards-- we worked for them, and sometimes I worked in the office where he was there, too.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was coming in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when we worked in his office, that was in [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Muszyna, ?] a little place close to the-- the-- that bordered on Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were four kilometers farther away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I came to [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Muszyna ?] to work for him, we had the bag with us because we had to work the whole day with the little piece of bread with us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When we were leaving for home, there was usually something in the back-- more bread-- that I assumed that Hans Joksch is the one that put it in, in our bag, putting it in.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there were some other things, some goodies, I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One time there was a bar of chocolate, or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He let us do all the work [INAUDIBLE] got some.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because he didn't want for the other ones to show that he was-- some privilege given to one Jewish girl, or two Jewish girls, Danka and I.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were dreaming of it, the assignment is gonna be there, so we have something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it wasn't always, every day, there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then one day we came there, and another time, and another time, and he wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
